or of dispersal limitation. Our findings provide a solid foundation for understanding the event-mediated processes of homogenization and present essential insights into how biogeographical and environmental factors affect different events on islands.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Li, Xianping", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bellard, C\u00e9line", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hu, Feng", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Li, Huixin", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 2", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1b38e28f4eae79bee4b11a25deb1a793", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/2609ab455d3aac0f4dc2ac5617646b2e289dd7048b8cfb1ee5187b6fb282579a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/TQ2JKJHG", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/TQ2JKJHG", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/bf5f57042bb005bdb35322253f65806f!/b103849-105946", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1002/ecs2.3008", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "e03008", "title": "Ecosphere", "volume": "11"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1b38e28f4eae79bee4b11a25deb1a793"}, {"id